{"tid":1061752,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家分享吓有咩歌係陪住自己長大","createTime":"2019-03-14T15:13:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T15:13:13.000Z","uid":186399,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"64486df0794bddd2e01a2138128e8b801bf16541","tid":1061752,"uid":186399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T15:13:13.000Z","msg":"好多歌都好鍾意聽，但就係有幾首係聽咗咁多年都唔厭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bg59q4puhmg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBg59q4puhmg&d=%2FIrJ3RR%2Fwz8SFLZOEAJhpvMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=f6c94b57\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bg59q4puhmg</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vx2u5uUu3DE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dvx2u5uUu3DE&d=%2FIrJ3RR%2Fwz8SFLZOEAJhpvMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=f18f5695\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vx2u5uUu3DE</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r00ikilDxW4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dr00ikilDxW4&d=%2FIrJ3RR%2Fwz8SFLZOEAJhpvMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=610ce0c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r00ikilDxW4</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ulOb9gIGGd0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DulOb9gIGGd0&d=%2FIrJ3RR%2Fwz8SFLZOEAJhpvMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=507d57b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ulOb9gIGGd0</a><br />\n上面哩幾首應該好多連登仔都聽過。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5abamRO41fE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5abamRO41fE&d=%2FIrJ3RR%2Fwz8SFLZOEAJhpvMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=1a7df933\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5abamRO41fE</a><br />\n但係Psychosocial連登應該比較少人識，利申自己唔係好識欣賞metal，但係哩首真係發泄神曲。首歌出既時候仲係小學雞，但就已經成日好多不滿，所以首歌對我真係好吸引，聽到而家都不時攞出來聽。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過聽聽吓有時都會唸，咁就十年過咗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}